{"TopicId":218438,"ForumId":70,"TopicTitle":"[Solution] AVP clouds glitch","CreatedByName":"BlackBourn","CreatedById":229904,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-15T20:40:28Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"BlackBourn","CreatedById":229904,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-15T20:40:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello!\u003Cbr\u003E\nUsing AVP I discovered a bug with the clouds, they seem to be stuck to the camera, and after i leave the atmosphere, the atmosphere and clouds start to behave strangely.\u003Cbr\u003E\nThis annoyed me so I spent a few hours experimenting with adding and removing mods and found a solution\u003Cbr\u003E\nThe reason for this error is the latest version of TUFX 1.0.6.0\u003Cbr\u003E\nInstalling version 1.0.4.0 or older fixes this problem!\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\nI\u00A0hope this advice will be helpful for you \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022VDTtHfB.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022120.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/VDTtHfB.png\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022RfyoULc.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022120.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/RfyoULc.png\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:8px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022LVdFkgX.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022120.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/LVdFkgX.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-07-16T20:31:48Z\u0022 title=\u002207/16/2023 08:31  PM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Jul 16\u0022\u003EJuly 16, 2023\u003C/